event.title: FSFE Infobooth at Suppe and Mucke in Berlin, Germany

body.p: The Berlin group of the FSFE will be represented with an informationbooth at the Friedrichshain soup festival ‘Suppe und Mucke’ on the RAW grounds on Saturday 15 June between 2 and 8 pm.

When: 15.06.2024, 14 bis 20 Uhr
Where: RAW Gelände Tor 1, Revalerstr. 99, Berlin
